Title: Grrilla
Body HTML:
Meet the Grrilla - our bristle-free grill scraper. Use this to avoid those traditional harmful bristle brushes that can shed metal wires and pose a health risk. Grrilla is laser cut from stainless steel, creating a dishwasher safe grilling accessory. This modern scraper is compatible with almost any model of charcoal, propane, and campground grills.
For gas grills - turn grill on to burn off residue, turn gas off to scrape remaining residue. Charcoal Grills - scrape off residue before lighting charcoal.

Title: Meat Charms
Body HTML: Keep track of the requested doneness level for each of your guests, on the grill and on the serving platter. Each pack consists of 6 charms: 2 Rare, 2 Medium Rare, 1 Medium, and 1 Medium Well. These laser cut stainless steel charms are food and dishwasher safe.

Title: Tangram Puzzle Coaster
Body HTML:
This set of 4 innovative drink coasters is perfect for parties, family gatherings, or just a cozy night in. Keep your furniture protected while challenging your mind with this interactive and engaging game.

Key Features:
  • Set of 4 absorbent coasters, designed to protect your surfaces from spills and condensation
  • Made of water-absorbent felt with a stain-resistant finish, ensuring a durable and lasting product
  • Cork bottom provides a non-slip surface, keeping your drinks steady and your table free from scratches
  • Each coaster features 7 removable puzzle pieces, designed to be assembled into a variety of Tangram shapes
  • 16+ games in one, offering endless hours of fun and mental stimulation
  • Play solo or engage in friendly competition with friends and family
  • Proudly made in the USA, ensuring high-quality craftsmanship

Challenge yourself or engage in friendly competition as you explore 16 unique Tangram puzzles. Each coaster has a hidden challenge, revealed by simply removing the puzzle pieces from the coaster's surface. Test your creativity and dexterity as you attempt to replicate animals and other intricate outlines provided on the inside of each coaster.

The Tangram Puzzle Coaster Set is an ideal gift for those who appreciate both style and entertainment. Whether it's for a housewarming, birthday, or just a thoughtful gesture, this set is sure to delight and impress. Elevate your next gathering or bring a touch of whimsy to your daily routine with this exciting and functional conversation piece. Order your set today and immerse yourself in the captivating world of Tangram puzzles!

Title: Northstar Notebook
Body HTML: A notebook worthy of being carried everywhere you go. It contains 160 pages dotted with a subtle grid pattern for ease of note-taking and sketching. Measuring 5 by 9 inches, this notebook is perfectly sized for portability without compromising on writing space. A distinguishing feature is the leather magnetic strip latch that ensures your pages remain undisturbed and even incorporates a convenient pen holder. Designed for durability, versatility, and style, the Northstar Notebook is your steadfast companion at work, home, or on the trail.

Title: The Rift Belt™- Stainless
Body HTML: The Rift Belt uses a patent-pending "rift" slot for infinite adjustability with quick connect, disconnect, and friction-locks without any slippage. Laser cut from Stainless Steel and Abrasion Resistant Nylon, the belt is built to look fashionable day in and day out. This belt is One-Size-Fits-Most up to a 50" waist. It can be worn as is or can also be cut to length with scissors and seared with a flame.

Title: The Rift Wallet™ - Slim Metal RFID-Blocking
Body HTML:
With the capacity to hold more than 10 credit and ID cards, as well as cash folded twice, the Rift Wallet's flexible design accommodates your needs without adding unnecessary bulk. The metal exterior not only exudes a sense of modern sophistication but also provides RFID protection, ensuring your sensitive card information remains safe from wireless skimming threats.
The innovative two-finger hole feature sets the Rift Wallet apart from the rest. Effortlessly push your cards up with two fingers, then pinch between the finger holes to "pop" the cards up and fan them out, allowing you to quickly and easily access the card you need.
Upgrade your carry game with the Rift Wallet – the perfect fusion of security, functionality, and sleek design for those who appreciate a minimalist approach to their everyday essentials.

Title: Calypso Crossbody
Body HTML: Finally, a bag that is just right - plenty of pockets, while being light and perfectly sized. Made from recycled plastic water bottles, this bag has four pockets on the outside, so you can easily store and access your phone, keys, wallet, or water bottle. The bright colors will make you stand out from the crowd, while the sailing rope shoulder strap adds a touch of nautical charm.

Title: Dockside Tote
Body HTML: Whether you're heading to work or out for a day trip, this tote has you tot-ally covered. Made from waterproof fabric and reinforced with sturdy rope handles, the Dockside Tote is ready to take on any challenge. Its bright colors and nautical design evoke a sense of seaside or lakeside charm, while the open top and spacious interior make it easy to access your essentials.

Title: Fearless Crossbody
Body HTML:
The Fearless Crossbody is equally suited for your daily routine or venturing into the great outdoors. Made from up-cycled plastic water bottles, its water-repellent fabric is both lightweight and durable, ensuring it stands up to life's adventures. The handy open-top dual pocket at the back of the bag, concealed against your body when carried, provides quick access to essentials like your phone, wallet, and keys. An additional outer zipper pocket adds extra organization for on-the-go convenience.

This sleek and stylish bag is designed to keep you organized, prepared, and confident as you conquer the world. Embrace your inner power and chase your dreams with the Fearless Crossbody by your side. Remember, you are not an imposter – you are a force to be reckoned with. Let this bag be your daily reminder to face challenges head-on and show the world what you're truly capable of. Be bold, be strong, be fearless.

Crossbody bags have taken the world by storm, and the Fearless Crossbody is no exception, exuding both excitement and functionality. Meticulously laser-cut and handmade in Maine, this phenomenal bag is a testament to quality craftsmanship and an empowering companion for the unstoppable woman.

Title: Sidewinder Sling
Body HTML:
This over-the-shoulder sling bag effortlessly adapts to your needs, resting high on your back, across the chest, or worn as a waist "fanny pack". Made with brightly colored water-resistant nylon fabric and accented by a diagonal black zipper, the Sidewinder Sling seamlessly combines fashion and functionality.

Unisex in its appeal, this bag is perfect for active, travel-savvy individuals seeking a practical and trendy accessory for their journeys. Choose the Sidewinder Sling and elevate your everyday adventures with a trusty companion by your side.

Title: Trail Notes
Body HTML: This thoughtfully designed notebook measures 5 by 9 inches and offers 160 pages of dot grid sheets, providing an ideal canvas for your notes, sketches, or journal entries. Its cover, crafted from waterproof nylon fabric, ensures durability and protection. The addition of a pen holder means your writing instrument is always within reach, while an elastic band secures your contents, keeping your notebook neatly closed when not in use. Elevate your note-taking experience with Trail Notes.

Title: City Venture Tote
Body HTML:
Crafted from durable, high-quality materials, the Venture Tote is built to withstand the rigors of travel, work, and play. Its generous interior offers ample space for all your essentials, from daily necessities to unexpected finds during your excursions. With convenient deep external pockets, you can easily organize and access your belongings, ensuring a seamless journey wherever you go.
Inspired by the spirit of exploration, the Venture Tote features a timeless design that complements any outfit or occasion. Whether you're heading to the office, embarking on a weekend getaway, or exploring new horizons, this tote bag will be your trusted ally.
Embrace the spirit of adventure and elevate your everyday style with the Venture Tote – the perfect fusion of fashion, function, and freedom.

Title: Voyager Daypack
Body HTML:
Crafted from high-quality, lightweight materials, the Voyager Pack is designed to withstand the elements and be the "right bag" for your everyday use. Featuring a roll-top closure with an adjustable strap and clip, this backpack ensures your belongings remain safe and secure in all conditions. The waterproof zipper pocket and open exterior pockets provide quick and easy access to your essentials, while the spacious main compartment includes an inner laptop sleeve for added protection and organization.
For maximum comfort during your travels, the Voyager Pack boasts two thick, durable nylon webbing straps, an adjustable chest strap, and felt pads with a relief for the spine, providing ergonomic support for even the most demanding excursions.
Embrace your inner adventurer and elevate your everyday style with the Voyager Pack – the epitome of fashion-forward, practical design for those who dare to explore the world.

Title: Custom Map Aluminum Coaster
Body HTML:
Each coaster in this set of 4 is meticulously crafted from 6061 aircraft-grade aluminum, showcasing exceptional durability and a premium feel that's sure to impress your guests. Finished with a sleek black ceramic coating, these coasters not only protect your surfaces from spills and scratches but also serve as a conversation starter. What sets these coasters apart is the intricate laser engraving that captures a street and terrain map of your chosen location, transforming your favorite place into a piece of functional art.
Whether it's your hometown, the city where you met your partner, or the destination of your most cherished memories, the Custom Map Aluminum Coasters pay tribute to the places that hold a special place in your heart. These coasters make a thoughtful gift for friends and loved ones or a unique statement piece for your own home.
Celebrate the places that matter most with the Custom Map Aluminum Coasters – a perfect blend of form, function, and sentiment that elevates your everyday living space.

Title: Tūlry 8-in-1 Stainless Necklace
Body HTML:
Embrace the synergy of style and utility with a collection that captures the essence of nature and philosophy in a series of elegant, yet functional, accessories. Choose from the strength of the bear, the majesty of the mountain, the serenity of the wave, the protection of the hamsa, or the balance of karma. Each design serves as a distinct cover, adding a touch of personality while concealing the useful tools beneath.

Hidden behind these captivating designs, the second pendant reveals five different hex keys, a miniaturized solution to handle hex head bolts and screws typically needing a set of allen keys. The third pendant holds a secret of its own: a useful pry-bar and a Phillips screwdriver. These essential tools ensure that, whether it's a refreshing drink you need to open or a minor repair job you need to tackle, you're always prepared without compromising on your style statement.

All these elements hang beautifully on an 18-inch chain, allowing the Tūlry pendant necklace to seamlessly blend with your outfit while providing the added advantage of a mini-toolbox at your disposal.

The Zootility 8-in-1 Tūlry Pendant Necklace Set goes beyond conventional accessories. It's a testament to innovative design and the potential of integrating style with functionality. With this unique necklace set, you carry a part of nature, a piece of philosophy, and a handful of essential tools wherever you go. Proudly MADE IN USA.

Body HTML:
Your secret arsenal of tools, beautifully disguised as an elegant accessory. Each Tūlry necklace consists of three layered stainless steel pendants, carefully crafted to blend practicality with aesthetics. Hidden behind the starry veil, the second pendant carries five distinct hex keys, providing a compact solution to turning hex head bolts and screws that would typically require a set of allen keys. The third pendant in this versatile ensemble boasts a pry-bar and a Phillips screwdriver.

All these functional layers hang gracefully on an 18-inch chain, making the Tūlry necklace a perfect blend of style, subtlety, and functionality. It's an accessory that not only enhances your outfit but also stands by you in times of need.

The Zootility 8-in-1 Tūlry Pendant Necklace is more than just a jewelry piece; it's a testament to the versatility of design. Embrace the intersection of fashion and practicality with this unique necklace, and carry your zodiac sign and your toolset wherever you go. Proudly MADE IN USA.

Title: Elastic Phone Wallet - Prints
Body HTML:
Designed for both Apple and Android phones, as well as most phone cases, this two-card holder seamlessly attaches to your device, providing convenience and style without the bulk of a traditional wallet. Installation is a breeze – simply peel back the adhesive protector and secure the wallet to the back of your phone. The magnetic disconnect feature allows you to effortlessly remove your wallet whenever you need to use a car mount or wireless charger, ensuring your on-the-go lifestyle remains uninterrupted.
One of the standout features of the Magnetic Phone Wallet is the ingenious edge design that catches the sticker backing, preventing the wallet from accidentally sliding off your phone and getting lost. This clever detail provides an extra layer of security and peace of mind for the user.
Upgrade your carry game with the Magnetic Phone Wallet – the perfect fusion of convenience, style, and functionality for those who demand efficiency and simplicity in their everyday essentials.

Title: Fishing Survival Kit
Body HTML:
Crafted in the dimensions of a credit card, this highly portable, multi-tool survival kit equips you with the essential tools needed to face an unforeseen wilderness encounter.
  • 4 x Fish hooks
  • De-scaler
  • 2 x Lures / traps
  • 5ft x Fishing line
  • Saw Blade
  • Tweezers
  • 2 x Screwdrivers

The Fishing Survival Kit features four razor-sharp fishing hooks, expertly designed for securing your next meal. Our kit includes two enticing lures and five feet of strong, durable fishing line to aid in your survival fishing efforts. Additionally, a descaling tool is seamlessly integrated into the design, ensuring your catch is meal-ready in no time.

Beyond its fishing-focused tools, the Zootility Fishing Survival Kit comes with a sharp utility blade that can be used for a multitude of purposes, from preparing food to crafting other survival necessities. The kit's dual-functioning screwdrivers are built to assist in making necessary adjustments to your gear or constructing shelter. Lastly, the tweezers included can prove invaluable for first aid situations, such as removing splinters or thorns.

The genius of the Zootility Fishing Survival Kit lies in its magnetic closure mechanism. This innovative design allows for easy and secure storage of the tools in their credit card-sized case. The kit fits effortlessly in your wallet, making it an unintrusive companion for all your adventures.

With the Zootility Fishing Survival Kit, you won't just survive – you'll thrive. Remember, in a survival situation, it's not just about the tools you have but the knowledge and determination you possess. So, be prepared and carry confidence in your pocket with the Zootility Fishing Survival Kit – MADE IN USA.

Despite the comprehensive tool options, the Hexalotl remains sleek and compact, fitting perfectly on your keychain without adding unnecessary bulk. It's a testament to smart design, ensuring you have a broad spectrum of tools available without compromising on convenience or portability.

With the Zootility 10-in-1 Hexalotl Multi-Tool, you're not just carrying a tool, you're carrying a toolbox and a trusty companion. Embrace the whimsy and functionality of this unique multi-tool, and turn everyday tasks into joyful experiences. Proudly MADE IN USA.

Title: ParaKEYd™ 9-in-1 Multi-Tool
Body HTML:
A robust key-sized multi-tool that's not only handy but also a delightful conversation starter. Shaped like a parrot, this keychain tool provides an array of essential tools without weighing you down.
  • 3 x hex wrenches
  • 2 x screwdrivers
  • Handle for hex driver bits
  • Bottle opener
  • Pry bar
  • Ruler

The ParaKEYd offers three distinct hex wrench sizes, ideal for tightening nuts and bolts, making it a handy partner in on-the-go repairs. It also features a sturdy driver handle compatible with hex drill bits, broadening your ability to handle an array of fix-it scenarios.
Incorporated into the design are screwdrivers that are always at the ready. Whether it's a flathead or a Philips, the ParaKEYd has got you covered.
Further enhancing the ParaKEYd's utility, a sturdy pry bar is artfully integrated into the design. This tool can help you open lids, remove nails, or perform a multitude of tasks that require a little bit of leverage.
A built-in ruler allows for quick and convenient measurements, ensuring you're never left guessing. And, after a long day of fixes and measurements, you can unwind with the help of the ParaKEYd's integrated bottle opener.
All these features are neatly packed into the shape of a parrot, creating a unique keychain tool that's both fun and functional. The Zootility 9-in-1 ParaKEYd turns any keyring into a toolbox without adding bulk.
With the Zootility 9-in-1 ParaKEYd, you're not just carrying a tool - you're carrying a solution. Enjoy a new level of preparedness and versatility with this playful yet practical addition to your everyday carry. Proudly MADE IN USA.

Title: Sewing Survival Kit
Body HTML:
This credit card-sized survival kit puts essential sewing tools at your fingertips, all in a compact and convenient format that slides right into your wallet.
  • 3 x Large buttons
  • 4 x Small buttons
  • Ruler
  • Safety pin
  • Needles
  • Thread
  • Screwdrivers

This kit includes safety pins, invaluable for temporary repairs, securing bandages, or even gear modifications. Alongside this, the kit features an assortment of small and large buttons, ensuring you're prepared to mend any garment mishap.
Organized in a sleek, credit-card-sized case with a secure magnetic closure, making this kit an unintrusive addition to your daily carry.
With the Zootility Sewing Survival Kit, you're not just prepared - you're self-sufficient. Stay equipped and ready to face the unexpected with the convenience and assurance of this nifty survival kit. Proudly MADE IN USA.

Title: Turtool™ 14-in-1 Keychain Multi-Tool
Body HTML:
With the Zootility Turtool, you're not just carrying a multi-tool; you're carrying a compact toolbox right on your keyring.
  • 9 x Hex wrenches
  • 4 x Hex keys
  • Phillips Screwdriver
  • Bottle Opener

The Turtool features an impressive array of nine hex wrenches in varying sizes. Adding to its wide-ranging functionality, the Turtool also includes five distinct screwdrivers. Whether you're dealing with a Philips or a flathead screw, the Turtool has got you covered, making minor repairs a breeze no matter where you are.
But the Turtool isn't just about work; it's also about enjoyment. Integrated into the design is a trusty bottle opener, ready to assist in popping open a refreshing beverage at the end of a long day.
Despite its robust functionality, the Turtool maintains a compact, key-sized form. Crafted in the charming shape of a turtle, it adds personality to your everyday carry without adding bulk.
Embrace the convenience and practicality of having a versatile solution always at hand with this adorable yet robust addition to your everyday carry. Proudly MADE IN USA.

Title: WildCard® Survival Kit
Body HTML:
Your ticket to self-reliance and survival, all packed into the slim profile of a credit card, including a replacement blade for our popular WildCard pocket knife.
  • Saw edge
  • Arrowhead
  • Tweezers
  • 2 x Fish hooks
  • WildCard replacement blade
  • 2 x Screwdrivers

The kit also includes two sharp fishing hooks, giving you the ability to tap into aquatic resources for sustenance. The arrowhead, another essential survival tool in the kit, can be used for hunting, self-defense, or even to create other tools necessary for survival.
Integrated into the kit are a pair of tweezers, an unassuming but crucial tool for first aid. Whether it's removing splinters, thorns, or ticks, these tweezers can help keep small injuries from turning into major problems.
Rounding off the kit are two durable screwdrivers. Handy for gear repair, constructing shelters, or numerous other survival tasks, these tools highlight the thoughtfulness put into this survival kit.
The entire set comes neatly housed in a credit-card-sized case that features our innovative magnetic closure mechanism, ensuring secure storage and easy access. Perfect for your wallet or pocket, the Zootility WildCard Survival Kit embodies the principles of preparedness and versatility.
With the WildCard Survival Kit by Zootility, you're not just prepared, you're empowered. Embrace the wilderness with confidence knowing you have a reliable partner at your side. Proudly MADE IN USA.

Title: Wilderness Survival Kit
Body HTML:
Compact yet powerful, this survival kit, taking up no more space than a standard credit card, carries the essential tools you need to face any unexpected wilderness situation.
  • Saw
  • Tweezers
  • Arrowhead
  • 2 x Fire starter flints
  • 2 x Fishing hooks
  • 2 x Lures


The Wilderness Survival Kit comes equipped with two sharp fishing hooks and two lures, setting you up for a successful fishing endeavor. The kit makes food procurement a less daunting task, turning any nearby water body into a potential food source.
In addition to its fishing tools, the Wilderness Survival Kit features a meticulously designed arrow tip, a critical tool for hunting small game or for use in self-defense. The arrow tip can be affixed to a makeshift shaft, creating a reliable tool for hunting and protection.
The kit also sports a pair of fire starting flints. Simply insert the flints into the circular holder and strike with a rock. Sparks can catch dry grasses on fire and provide an essential tool in a survival situation.
An invaluable asset in any survival scenario, the kit includes a 3-inch saw blade. Whether you need to construct a shelter, gather firewood, or create a signal for help, the saw blade is up for the task.
Last but not least, the kit contains a pair of tweezers, a tool often overlooked but essential for addressing minor first-aid needs like removing splinters or extracting ticks.
Housed in a sleek, credit-card-sized case with a magnetically secured closure, the Wilderness Survival Kit tucks easily into your wallet, making preparedness convenient and accessible.
The Zootility Wilderness Survival Kit is your testament to resilience in the face of adversity. With it in your pocket, you're not just equipped to survive; you're ready to prevail. Proudly MADE IN USA.

Title: Custom Map Serving Board
Body HTML: Expertly crafted from birch wood, our Custom Serving Board features 5-ply construction to prevent warping and boasts a navy blue paint finish. Title: Halo Wallet Prints
Body HTML: The Halo Wallet offers a no-frills solution for carrying essentials. Made with resilient elastic fabric, it boasts a long-lasting lifespan even when exposed to constant stretching. At an incredibly light weight, this wallet is easily portable and adheres to minimalist principles with its slim profile design. The stretchable fabric allows for versatile use, securely holding a variable amount of cards and cash. Proudly made in the USA, the Halo Wallet embodies both domestic craftsmanship and functional versatility, making it the top choice for those in need of a reliable and streamlined carry option.

Title: Pedestal Table Spinner

Title: Zootility Shopper Perks Vouchers
Body HTML: The Zootility Shopper Perks Program is designed to increase customer engagement and support our retail partners. Customers can receive a free Halo Wallet from Zootility when making qualifying purchases of $25+ at participating stores. The wallet can be personalized with laser-engraved text for an extra $8 fee. Stores get up to 25 vouchers per $500 spent with Zootility plus the option to purchase more for $25. Benefits include increased rate of sales, more store visits, self-service and enhanced customer loyalty through a unique, personalized gift. There's also social media engagement and a collaborative promotional effort.

Title: Custom Hyper Thin Wallet Knife
Body HTML:
The Hyper Thin Wallet Knife is the "World's Thinnest Pocket Knife". Same as our WildCard, but without the wolf shape. The patented FlyOff technology allows you to remove the blade quickly, and the handle also includes a set of tools:
  • Screwdrivers

Title: Custom Leather Phone Wallet
Body HTML:
Designed for any generation of Apple or Android phones, as well as most phone cases, this two-card holder seamlessly attaches to your device, providing convenience and style without the bulk of a traditional wallet. Installation is a breeze – simply peel back the adhesive protector and secure the wallet to the back of your phone. The magnetic disconnect feature allows you to effortlessly remove your wallet whenever you need to use a car mount or wireless charger.
One of the standout features of the Magnetic Phone Wallet is the ingenious edge design that catches the sticker backing, preventing the wallet from accidentally sliding off your phone and getting lost. This clever detail provides an extra layer of security and peace of mind for the user.
Upgrade your carry game with the Magnetic Phone Wallet – the perfect fusion of convenience, style, and functionality for those who demand efficiency and simplicity in their everyday essentials.

Title: Custom Front Fold Wallet
Body HTML: This modern take on the classic fold wallet fits perfectly in your front pocket. Made from Genuine Leather, it uses elastic pockets to capture all your cards. Fold your bills twice to easily hold cash. Pockets open to the center, so nothing can slide out when closed.

Title: Custom Rift Wallet
Body HTML:
With the capacity to hold more than 10 credit and ID cards, as well as cash folded twice, the Rift Wallet's flexible design accommodates your needs without adding unnecessary bulk. The metal exterior not only exudes a sense of modern sophistication but also provides RFID protection, ensuring your sensitive card information remains safe from wireless skimming threats.
The innovative two-finger hole feature sets the Rift Wallet apart from the rest. Effortlessly push your cards up with two fingers, then pinch between the finger holes to "pop" the cards up and fan them out, allowing you to quickly and easily access the card you need.
Upgrade your carry game with the Rift Wallet – the perfect fusion of security, functionality, and sleek design for those who appreciate a minimalist approach to their everyday essentials.

Title: Gator-Done™ 14-in-1 Keychain Multi-Tool
Body HTML:
With the Zootility Gator-Done, you're not just carrying a multi-tool; you're carrying a compact toolbox right on your keyring.

  • 9 x Hex wrenches
  • 4 x Hex keys
  • Phillips Screwdriver
  • Bottle Opener


The Gator-Done features an impressive array of nine hex wrenches in varying sizes. Adding to its wide-ranging functionality, the Gator-Done also includes five distinct screwdrivers. Whether you're dealing with a Philips or a flathead screw, the Gator-Done has got you covered, making minor repairs a breeze no matter where you are.
But the Gator-Done isn't just about work; it's also about enjoyment. Integrated into the design is a trusty bottle opener, ready to assist in popping open a refreshing beverage at the end of a long day.
Despite its robust functionality, the Gator-Done maintains a compact, key-sized form. Crafted in the charming shape of an alligator, it adds personality to your everyday carry without adding bulk.
Embrace the convenience and practicality of having a versatile solution always at hand with this adorable yet robust addition to your everyday carry. Proudly MADE IN USA.
